{{Orphan|date=September 2015}}
This is a '''list of public art''' on permanent public display in [[São Paulo]], [[São Paulo (State)]], [[Brazil]].
The list applies only to works of [[public art]] accessible in an outdoor public space; it does not include artwork on display inside museums. Public art may include [[sculpture]]s, [[statue]]s, [[monument]]s, [[memorial]]s, [[mural]]s and [[mosaic]]s.
This list does not include military and war memorials.
