'''''The Best American Short Stories 1987''''', a volume in ''[[The Best American Short Stories]] series'', was edited by guest editor [[Ann Beattie]] with Shannon Ravenel.<ref>Beattie, Ann and Shannon Ravenel (editors), ''The Best American Short Stories 1987'', Boston: Houghton Mifflin Co, 1987.</ref>
